Name: Peoples Federal Bancshares, Inc
Description: DELISTED - Peoples Federal Bancshares, Inc. will become the holding company of Peoples Federal Savings Bank upon completion of the mutual-to-stock conversion. Peoples Federal Savings Bank is a wholly owned subsidiary of Peoples Federal Bancorp, Inc. As of March 17, 2010, Peoples Federal Bancshares, Inc. was not engaged in any business. Peoples Federal Savings Bank is a federally chartered savings bank. Peoples Federal Bancorp, Inc. is a wholly owned subsidiary of Peoples Federal MHC, a federal mutual holding company. Pursuant to the terms of Peoples Federal MHC's plan of conversion and reorganization, Peoples Federal MHC will convert from a mutual holding company to the stock holding company corporate structure. Upon the completion of the conversion, Peoples Federal MHC and Peoples Federal Bancorp, Inc. will cease to exist, and Peoples Federal Savings Bank will be a wholly owned subsidiary of Peoples Federal Bancshares, Inc.
